---
title: Archives
layout: main
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 30
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
---
<p>A collection of all my writings in one place (daily + long form posts)</p>
{% for post in posts %}
<div class=blog-link>
<a href="{{post.url}}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
</div>
<hr>
{% endfor %}

<p>
{% if pagination.href.previous %}
<a href=" {{ pagination.href.previous }}">Previous</a>
{% else %}
Previous
{% endif %} 
/ 
{% if pagination.href.next %}
<a href=" {{ pagination.href.next }}">Next</a>
{% else %}
Next
{% endif %}
</p>